# Runtime
reasoning_effort: low
verbosity: low

Return valid JSON only.

Schema:
{
  "issues": [
    {
      "string_id": "",
      "issue_type": "terminology|fluency|truncation|placeholder_error|tone|other",
      "severity": "low|medium|high",
      "explanation": "",
      "suggested_fix": ""
    }
  ]
}

<localized_strings>
{{LOCALIZED_STRINGS}}
</localized_strings>

System Instruction: Extract all contact information from the provided text. Return only valid JSON. Use null for missing fields.

User: Extract contacts from this text:

{{TEXT}}

